telling me this?

774
01:09:19,615 --> 01:09:21,697
A lot of what Blackwood wrote
at the end of his life,

775
01:09:21,784 --> 01:09:23,945
it's awfully close
to Sally's story,

776
01:09:24,036 --> 01:09:25,776
gnomes, creatures,
all of it.

777
01:09:25,872 --> 01:09:27,282
