787
01:10:02,617 --> 01:10:04,949
Come on, Sally.
Get in the car.

788
01:10:08,789 --> 01:10:10,700
Sally, please,
just tonight,

789
01:10:10,791 --> 01:10:12,782
and after the party
we'll talk, okay?

790
01:10:37,485 --> 01:10:40,101
Four, three,

791
01:10:40,196 --> 01:10:42,812
two and one.

792
01:10:44,492 --> 01:10:45,481
There.

793
01:10:47,536 --> 01:10:50,323
After the party, I will
get you out of here.

794
01:10:50,498 --> 01:10:52,159
No matter what.
I promise.

795
01:10:58,881 --> 01:11:00,667
- Sally!
- No.

796
01:11:00,841 --> 01:11:02,126
