bright lights.

804
01:11:31,163 --> 01:11:32,323
Those things.

805
01:11:33,040 --> 01:11:34,029
They don't?

806
01:11:39,088 --> 01:11:40,419
Then I have
a good idea.

807
01:11:46,429 --> 01:11:48,135
