Come on in.

811
01:11:53,477 --> 01:11:57,015
The house looks
absolutely fantastic.

812
01:11:57,189 --> 01:11:58,520
You've done
a remarkable job.

813
01:11:58,691 --> 01:12:00,898
Well, thank you.

814
01:12:01,068 --> 01:12:02,228
