of Fallen Mill,

850
01:14:12,158 --> 01:14:14,240
both big and small.

851
01:14:14,326 --> 01:14:16,442
Thank you for joining
us this evening.

852
01:14:16,537 --> 01:14:17,947
It means a great
deal to us.

853
01:14:18,831 --> 01:14:23,495
Every aspect of this restoration
has followed the exact specifications

854
01:14:23,586 --> 01:14:26,749
and materials used in the
original construction of the house,

855
01:14:26,922 --> 01:14:30,756
